&lt;h1 id="advice-for-students--especially-graduate-students-in-statistics"&gt;Advice for Students &amp;mdash; Especially Graduate Students in Statistics&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This page summarizes a discussion at the &lt;a href="http://www-stat.wharton.upenn.edu/~steele/GradStudentSeminar/"&gt;Graduate Student Lunch Time Seminar&lt;/a&gt; (1/29/2007). My intention was to put on the table the best practical advice I could muster, spiced up with some general musings about mentoring, writing, and publishing.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>